{"type": "article", "id": 43543, "title": "饮料做成这样，都是治愈夏日烦躁的良药｜这个设计了不起", "description": "每个周末，《好奇心日报》都会找个主题为你寻找精彩设计。", "date": "2017-07-28T23:49:20Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 3875, "name": "包装设计"}, {"id": 34187, "name": "Futura"}, {"id": 38070, "name": "The Studio"}, {"id": 42782, "name": "LMNOP Creative"}, {"id": 42783, "name": "Marx Design"}, {"id": 42784, "name": "山形食品"}], "category": 17, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 16, "praise_count": 505, "image": "img/article/article_show/20170729005205WHfMRSs26hYtlNwO.jpg", "contents": "<p nocleanhtml=\"true\">        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #323333} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #323333; min-height: 25.0px} p.p3 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 27.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636} p.p4 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 27.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636; min-height: 25.0px} p.p5 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 12.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #323333} p.p6 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 12.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #323333; min-height: 25.0px} p.p7 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 27.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #323333} p.p8 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 27.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #323333; min-height: 25.0px} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} span.s2 {font-kerning: none; color: #323333} span.s3 {font-kerning: none; color: #363636} </style>  </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。<br></p><p>一进入盛夏，平时用来让自己远离各种软饮料的借口似乎都不那么管用了。在烈日下走上一段路，就想着用那些清凉的液体滋润喉咙。本周我们整理了一些看着就很凉爽的包装，请自备饮料阅读。</p><h3>Dose by Nora Kaszanyi</h3><p>用“能够治愈夏日烦躁感的一剂良药”来形容匈牙利设计师 <a href=\"https://www.behance.net/norakaszanyi\" rel=\"nofollow\">Nora Kaszanyi</a> 打造的概念汽水品牌 Dose 或许并不夸张。抛开意为“剂量”的品牌名不谈，将一半透明一半选择水果代表色的瓶子侧放后，你就能发现它其实酷似一枚胶囊。擅长简约风的 Kaszanyi 在处理标签时也特意选择了文字寥寥的表格形式，你还可以在左上角找到标有维生素的格子。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170729005257bHKn4M6wjgqh2NPf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170729005257uF8v32OgHjEGqPCm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.628333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170729005259efFb8ISrmNCxjWQv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.685833\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170729005258sVFKHekQnTrCAyPY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.641667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>&amp;Pizza soda by Futura</h3><p>还记得那个<a href=\"http://www.qdaily.com/articles/31144.html\">靠包装走红的柠檬水</a>吗？墨西哥创意机构 <a href=\"http://byfutura.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Futura</a> 为美国连锁餐厅 <a href=\"http://www.andpizza.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">&amp;Pizza</a> 设计的手工汽水包装也选择了让人难以琢磨的风格。我们之前曾介绍过他们为餐厅设计的<a href=\"http://www.qdaily.com/articles/33599.html\">披萨盒</a>，尽管街头风并没有延续到汽水系列中，这些几何图案依然相当耐看，看起来就好像是某个拼图的一部分。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170729005325OIEDxkdPomtp9KRu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.649167\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170729005327So1icl45MgNyLKzs.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170729005327wXqVWygEHjvfMzr8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170729005329GF8tsgVaP5rNL3JR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>StrangeLove by Marx Design</h3><p>人们愿意为高颜值的汽水瓶发照片，但相同的事情似乎很少发生在功能饮料上，由新西兰设计公司 <a href=\"http://www.marxdesign.co.nz/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Marx Design</a> 操刀形象设计的澳大利亚品牌 <a href=\"http://www.strangelove.com.au/\" rel=\"nofollow\">StrangeLove</a> 则证明了这种饮料并非与 Instagrammable 一词无缘。清新的配色、留白、古灵精怪的配图……这些少见于功能饮料的视觉元素勾起了人们去解读每个细节的欲望，标签背面的一小段饮料介绍也藏了不少有趣的梗。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170729005348e3cXHdMD5EYLnTOu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.704444\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170729005346CYF5OwR7cpM1ZIJX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.833333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170729005346mQsMrCc86BgxHR5W.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170729005346VurY6dPSfpQRKgsC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Lemonaid by The Studio</h3><p>来自德国的 <a href=\"http://www.lemon-aid.de/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Lemonaid</a> 是一个希望通过生产和销售软饮料带来社会变革的慈善机构：他们的材料遵循公平贸易采购自合作的小型果园，每售出一瓶柠檬水或是冰茶（Charitea）都会捐出一笔资金用于各种援助项目，善款到目前为止已经累计<a href=\"http://handmade-worldtour.com/en/exhibition/lemonaid/\" rel=\"nofollow\">超过 74 万欧元</a>。基于产品的特殊性，瑞典设计工作室 <a href=\"http://the-studio.se/\" rel=\"nofollow\">The Studio</a> 为其设计了一个非常直白的包装，logo 则采用了象征援助的十字，希望借此让它从货架上脱颖而出。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2017072900563932RcefraAKLBiO9b.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.712500\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170729005640GztRwZ9nJUdfjP3i.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.712500\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170729005641t6VNLkaD2eb3fSmT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562500\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170729005644FDiUEyHOYBvef9lu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562500\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Seriously Unsweetened by LMNOP Creative</h3><p>Seriously Unsweetened 是纽约饮料制造商 Tiny Kitchen Brands 推出的气泡水品牌，由来自布鲁克林的创意团队 <a href=\"http://www.lmnopcreative.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">LMNOP</a> 负责形象设计。为了强调天然、无糖这样的概念，LMNOP 在设计瓶身时显得格外克制，三种风味仅通过简单的气泡和水果插图表现。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201707290054096hU1lkOqyWVz5xev.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.710000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170729005413d0qAj13CHDnrf8mi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.420000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170729005414i3tHGW0X6CMSjbTs.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.710000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Soda &amp; Cider by 山形食品</h3><p>2013 年三月，一罐名为“みずいろの雨”的鸡尾酒味汽水让日本山形县的饮料制造商<a href=\"http://www.ym-foods.co.jp/index.html\" rel=\"nofollow\">山形食品</a>出了名。它的设计灵感来源于日本歌手八神纯子的同名代表曲，白色罐身上的蓝色雨滴刚好对应了标题所指的“水色的雨”。在此之后，山形食品还推出了用当地特色水果制成的“果物汽水”系列，包括用黑色星光模仿西瓜籽的尾花沢西瓜味。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170729005428iXBTx5OKWu8qjd2v.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170729005429Eh5kiKnuJm80r4AT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170729005429wXu2Nmc4Le97IyBr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.998958\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170729005429jaAf6sNkW0JOoDYm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.572765\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div>"}